  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">EIDHR- Accompanying communities in processes of defence of human rights, water and territory,</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project is the Colombia third party grant component of a regional HRD project that aims to support and protect human right defenders at risk working on land and environmental rights in Latin America. It is focused in the Meta region, where a community led by women human rights defenders is trying to protect its territory and in particular the water sources from the negative impacts of fossil fuel (oil) exploitation.</narrative>
  </description>
